{
  "stem": "11882.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We landed in the Azores, and there the soldiers always had terrible stories to tell us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The last plane-- soldiers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The last plane-- you know, civilians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The last plane that came through here, well, it took off all right, but it went right down, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all these stories, you know, you had no way of knowing is it true or isn't it true.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the soldiers loved to tell these serious, sad stories to us so-called civilians that were going to sail on somewhere better than they were, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we arrived then in Paris at Orly Field and went to the Majestic Hotel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was occupied by the American Army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all-- we were eight or nine people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I say, there was one lieutenant in charge of us, and we had a very peppy middle-aged lady that was older than the rest of us at that time, and she kind of took charge.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She knew intelligent things to do like go to the desk, and find the Army man that will know when the next train to Frankfurt goes, you know, and how we can get on it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we got onto a train to Frankfurt that was heading toward Nuremberg, and it took 20 hours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It stopped more than it started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was ice cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't heated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All along, the buildings were all bombed out, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And everything was in disarray and disorganization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We got to Frankfurt, and the whole city was bombed out, rubble, and soldiers patrolling before the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a nice cafeteria where military employees could go in the IG Farbon building, and nobody else could go in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everything very isolated, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
